    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's really strong stuff, thanks. my students are worried about the counter-arguments though. they're getting a lot of pushback that these views are just driven by fear or xenophobia rather than actual logic. how should they respond to the claim that stricter enforcement is just a way to marginalize certain groups? can you help them flip that script so they don't look like they're just being reactionary?",
